<s1>Special Characters

The following list shows the special characters that you can use with HP
HelpTag.  To include any of these characters, enter the entity reference
shown.

<image>

<esc><SIZE 14><\esc> &MINUS; <esc></><\esc> (``\&&minus;'')

<esc><SIZE 14><\esc> &PM; <esc></><\esc> (``\&&pm;'')

<esc><SIZE 14><\esc> &DIV; <esc></><\esc> (``\&&div;'')

