<s1>HP Help Application Programmer's Interface (API)

<term nogloss|NOTE:  Refer to the Cache Creek API External Specifications
for the latest API information!|


... introduction the API ...

<otherhead>Header Files

Before using any of the functions in the HP Help library, be sure
to include the appropriate header files:

<ex>
%%/* Required for all Xvh calls. */%%
#include \&<Xvh/Xvh.h>

%%/* Required if you use any help dialogs. */%%
#include \&<Xvh/HelpDialog.h>
<\ex>


<s2>Help Dialog Management Functions


... a description of the help dialogs provided by the CC library ...


... resources ...


<otherhead>For the Standard Help Dialog ...

<ex>
Widget  XvhCreateHelpDialog (
          Widget    %%parent%%,
          String    %%name%%,
          ArgList   %%argList%%,
          Cardinal  %%argCount%%
        )
<\ex>

<ex>
void  XvhHelpDialogSetTopic (
        Widget    %%helpDialog%%,
        String    %%locationID%%
      )
<\ex>

<ex>
void  XvhHelpDialogSetString (
        Widget    %%helpDialog%%,
        char     *%%string%%,
        char     *%%dialogTitle%%
      )
<\ex>

<ex>
void  XvhHelpDialogSetMan (
        Widget    %%helpDialog%%,
        char     *%%manString%%
      )
<\ex>

<otherhead>For the Quick Help Dialog ...

<ex>
Widget  XvhCreateQuickHelpDialog (
          Widget    %%parent%%,
          String    %%name%%,
          ArgList   %%argList%%,
          Cardinal  %%argCount%%
        )
<\ex>

<ex>
Widget  XvhQuickHelpDialogGetChild (
          Widget          %%helpDialog%%,
          unsigned char   %%child%%
        )
<\ex>

<otherhead>Utility Functions ...

<ex>
Widget  XvhReturnSelectedWidget(
          Widget  %%widget%%
        )
<\ex>

<ex>
Boolean  XvhGetTopicData (
           char            *%%filename%%, 
           char            *%%locationID%%, 
           int              %%maxColumns%%,
           char          ***%%helpTextList%%,
           XvhHyperLines  **%%hyperlinkList%%
         )
<\ex>

<ex>
Boolean  XvhProcessLinkData (
           XvhHyperLines   *%%hyperlinkList%%,
           char           **%%filename%%,
           char           **%%locationID%%
         )
<\ex>

<ex>
void  XvhFreeTopicData (
        char           **%%helpTextList%%,
        XvhHyperLines   *%%hyperlikList%%
      )
<\ex>




